ZH: 我们工作总是很忙。
EN: We are always very busy at work.

ZH: 他总喜欢独自一人旅行。
EN: He always likes to travel alone.

ZH: 她总是很认真地对待工作。
EN: She always takes her work very seriously.

ZH: 我们总是在周末一起去看电影。
EN: We always go watch movies together on weekends.

ZH: 他总是让我感到开心。
EN: He always makes me happy.

ZH: 你总是迟到，要不要改改？
EN: You are always late, do you want to change?

ZH: 她总是把家里收拾得很干净。
EN: She always keeps her house very clean.

ZH: 我们总是在这家餐厅吃晚饭。
EN: We always have dinner at this restaurant.

ZH: 他总是觉得自己很幸运。
EN: He always feels lucky.

ZH: 你们总是一群好朋友。
EN: You guys are always a great group of friends.

ZH: 我总是喜欢参加运动比赛。
EN: I always enjoy participating in sports competitions.

ZH: 她总是能够帮助我解决问题。
EN: She always helps me solve problems.

ZH: 他总是很有礼貌地对待别人。
EN: He always treats others with great politeness.

ZH: 我总是习惯在早上喝一杯咖啡。
EN: I always like to have a cup of coffee in the morning.

ZH: 他总是给我很多鼓励。
EN: He always gives me a lot of encouragement.

ZH: 她总是很乐于助人。
EN: She is always willing to help others.

ZH: 我们总是在假期去旅行。
EN: We always travel during holidays.

ZH: 他总是用热情对待每一个人。
EN: He always treats everyone with enthusiasm.

ZH: 你总是很有耐心地听我说。
EN: You always listen to me patiently.

ZH: 我们总是一起度过每一个节日。
EN: We always spend every holiday together.
